      "caption": "A year of realizations, memories, growth, and change.\n\nIt started with wrapping up my semester abroad in Istanbul. It ended with me completing my second bachelor\u2019s degree (finally graduated!!\ud83c\udf93\u2728)\n\nSomewhere in the middle of it all, I also embraced another part of me: the passion to know the unknown and make those soul connections that only happen beyond what\u2019s familiar. 25+ countries, countless experiences, and stories I\u2019ll take with me for life \u2764\ufe0f\u200d\ud83e\ude79\u267e\ufe0f\n\nSpecial thanks to my family and friends for supporting me, no matter the distance \ud83d\udc96\n\nTo everyone whose path crossed mine this year: forever grateful. 2025 reminded me that possibilities are endless when you keep moving forward (and believing in them) \ud83e\udef6\ud83c\udffb\u2b50\ufe0f\n\nExcited for 2026 (and for meeting the world \ud83d\uddfa\ufe0f\u2728)",
